{"tid":402624,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解有凶宅冇凶樓？","createTime":"2017-09-16T14:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T14:56:04.000Z","uid":143878,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"520d10f65cad0880d34ea73a066a0871c1a85772","tid":402624,"uid":143878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:44:14.000Z","msg":"如題，如果有人係某單位自殺，該單位就會變做凶宅，個價都平過人，唔介意既人可以買做上車盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但點解有人係某大廈既天台跳樓，該棟大廈又唔會叫做凶樓？<br />\n如果係既話 該樓樓價大跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，今次仲唔上到車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果地產佬因為唔想賺小左而唔作一個term叫凶樓，咁點解會出現凶宅一詞會出現去令到有機會降價<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係凶宅係買家諗出嚟既野？所以迫到凶宅要賤賣。咁不如我地一齊推廣凶樓個concept<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />買樓不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：冷血涼薄"},{"pid":"bda8f475649481f31a3239472b9d9ba37e59a403","tid":402624,"uid":146147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:51:51.000Z","msg":"係呀 到時公屋都唔流起架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ef2ea8df3f7be9f8212d41592b25dd4348df44","tid":402624,"uid":146147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:52:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係呀 到時公屋都唔流起架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n洗"},{"pid":"141364f96439c6455a607e37838fa150e2389ff8","tid":402624,"uid":130474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:56:04.000Z","msg":"有部份大廈多兇宅 / 好勁兇宅(即兇殺案),  的確會成坐平D......"}]}